data.description: Welcome to this charming home in the heart of Livonia! Located in the highly sought-after Stevenson School District. Boasting three bedrooms and the potential for a fourth with the added space upstairs, this home sits on a spacious double corner lot with two entrances, providing ample room for outdoor activities and future expansion. The main highlight is the completely updated full bath, featuring contemporary fixtures, sleek finishes, and a soothing ambiance. Fenced in yard and 1 car garage. Make this home your own! Welcome home.
